milestones.description: Australia's 278 is the highest total in ODIs, surpassing England's 266
Asif Iqbal and Wasim Raja's 77-run partnership is the highest for the 5th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 59 between Fletcher and Tony Greig
Dennis Lillee has become the top wicket-taker for AUS in ODIs with 10 wickets, going past Mallett's 8
Sarfraz Nawaz has conceded the most runs in an innings (63) in ODIs for PAK, going past Intikhab Alam's record of 58
Wasim Raja has broken the record for most catches (2) in ODIs for PAK, going past Saleem Altaf's 1
Majid Khan has scored 2 fifty-plus scores in ODIs, the most for PAK breaking Zaheer Abbas's record
Greg Chappell has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (8) for AUS, going past Ian Chappell
Asif Iqbal has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (4) for PAK, going past Asif Masood
Rick McCosker and Alan Turner's 63-run partnership is AUS's highest for the 1st wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 44 between Stackpole and Ross Edwards
Greg Chappell and Ross Edwards's 60-run partnership is AUS's highest for the 5th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 29 between Ian Redpath and Greg Chappell
Ross Edwards and Max Walker's 48-run partnership is AUS's highest for the 7th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 35 between Rod Marsh and Ross Edwards
Ross Edwards and Jeff Thomson's 35-run partnership is AUS's highest for the 8th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 17 between Mallett and Ross Edwards
Mushtaq Mohammad and Majid Khan's 41-run partnership is PAK's highest for the 3rd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 24 between Mushtaq Mohammad and Zaheer Abbas
Asif Iqbal and Wasim Raja's 77-run partnership is PAK's highest for the 5th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 22 between Mushtaq Mohammad and Wasim Raja
Imran Khan and Wasim Raja's 8-run partnership is PAK's highest for the 6th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 6 between Nasim-ul-Ghani and Mushtaq Mohammad
